msgstr "If this option is selected, menus open immediately."

#: general.cpp:426
msgid "If this option is selected, menus fade in slowly."
msgstr "If this option is selected, menus fade in slowly."

#: general.cpp:427
msgid "If this option is selected, menus are animated to grow to their full size."
msgstr "If this option is selected, menus are animated to grow to their full size."

#: general.cpp:428
msgid ""
"If this option is selected, combo boxes are animated to grow to their full "
"size."
msgstr ""
"If this option is selected, combo boxes are animated to grow to their full "
"size."

